Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.25,0:00:10.98,Translation,,0,0,0,,​​​GIRI GIRI, Let's get as close to being in love as we can​
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.05,0:00:14.75,Translation,,0,0,0,,​Set your lies ablaze and let dreams rise from it's ashes​
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.75,0:00:18.52,Translation,,0,0,0,,​I'm not joking, I want to dance with you even more​
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.54,0:00:22.06,Translation,,0,0,0,,I cannot hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.20,0:00:28.13,Translation,,0,0,0,,Your love, your love, confess your deep feelings of love
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.94,0:00:29.97,Translation,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:31.80,Translation,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.46,0:00:37.31,Translation,,0,0,0,,It really is dangerous, that smile of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.29,0:00:41.45,Translation,,0,0,0,,It disturbs me and at the same time, makes me desire you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.99,0:00:44.81,Translation,,0,0,0,,You a honor student? You're kidding, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.81,0:00:48.19,Translation,,0,0,0,,You keep evading and I'm becoming impatient!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:52.30,Translation,,0,0,0,,​I'm sure it will all work out somehow
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.30,0:00:56.03,Translation,,0,0,0,,But that won't be enough for our lips to touch together
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:57.90,Translation,,0,0,0,,I hold you close to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.77,Translation,,0,0,0,,We don't know what to do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.78,0:01:02.38,Translation,,0,0,0,,​You're staring at me with your lonely eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:05.41,Translation,,0,0,0,,I'm at my limit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.41,0:01:09.14,Translation,,0,0,0,,GIRA GIRA, Show me what you dream of the most​
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.12,0:01:12.90,Translation,,0,0,0,,​Scatter all your worries and let stars rise in their place
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:16.67,Translation,,0,0,0,,I want to see your not-so-innocent side even more​
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.67,0:01:20.45,Translation,,0,0,0,,​I cannot hold back anymore!​
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.35,0:01:23.24,Translation,,0,0,0,,​Your love, your love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.24,0:01:26.56,Translation,,0,0,0,,Confess your deep feelings of love
